reviewText: I love this show. Great cast, great writing. I love the characters, and characters they are, the plotting, the pacing.
Wrong region wrong information in ad no way to play it

Great show.  The writers find new ways to keep the script fresh.
Corporate vilification gets a bit tiresome but other than that, the filming is
inventive and the plots intriguing.  I can't quite give it a 5, but it's better
than a four.
I bought the first 4 seasons several years ago and thought that was all there was. Several months I found out that there were four more and was thrilled to obtain them.  This is a great series.
